# Code owners. With branch protection's "require review from Code Owners",
# changes to the privacy boundary and the supply chain cannot merge without an
# owner's approval — the property a security reviewer wants enforced, not just
# documented.

# Default owner for everything.
*                       @pa-arth

# --- Privacy boundary: what decides whether content leaves the machine ---
/internal/redact/       @pa-arth
/internal/event/        @pa-arth
/internal/sign/         @pa-arth
/internal/ingest/       @pa-arth

# --- Supply chain: build, release, install, distribution ---
/.github/               @pa-arth
/install.sh             @pa-arth
/Makefile               @pa-arth
/npm/                   @pa-arth

# --- Security-facing docs ---
/SECURITY.md            @pa-arth
